                                                    <p>3️⃣ Professional Email Writing – Structuring clear and concise emails for business communication.</p>
                                                    <p>4️⃣ Business Meetings & Presentations – Speaking with confidence and clarity in professional settings.</p>
                                                    <p>5️⃣ Negotiation & Persuasion Skills – Techniques for effective discussions and deal-making.</p>
                                                    <p>6️⃣ Telephone & Video Conferencing Etiquette – Mastering virtual communication in a business setting.</p>
                                                    <p>7️⃣ Final Assessment & Practice – Applying learned skills in real-world business scenarios.</p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="description-wrapper">
                                                    <h3 class="tab-title">Certification:</h3>
                                                    <p>Upon successful completion of the course, students will receive a Certificate of Completion, demonstrating their ability to communicate effectively in professional environments. This certificate can be added to resumes, LinkedIn profiles, or used for career advancement.</p>
                                                </div>
